 1. MODERN WARFARE / BATTLEFIELD CONTEXT:
    The spectral energy analysis identifies 'mechanical precision'
    in recoil patterns. A human broadens the spectrum (Thermal Noise); 
    a script narrows it to a single spike (Adversarial Oscillation).

 2. GTA / ECONOMY CONTEXT:
    Provenance failures (L3) combined with 'Impossible Transitions' 
    (L2.75) catch memory-injected inventory changes by verifying 
    every delta against the fixed-point lattice.

 3. PERSISTENCE SMOOTHING:
    By using the EMA, the system differentiates between a 'bad 
    connection' (brief desync) and a 'lag switch' (deliberate 
    causal interruption).
*/
